<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ881108-0053 </DOCNO><HL> Bow Valley to Buy Gas Assets </HL><SO> </SO><CO> BVI T.BZO </CO><IN> TNM </IN><DATELINE> CALGARY, Alberta  </DATELINE><TEXT>   Bow Valley Industries Ltd. said it agreed to purchase 54 million Canadian dollars (US$44 million) of oil and gas assets from Bonanza Oil andamp; Gas Ltd.    It said the transaction, expected to be completed by mid-January, involves the purchase of about 87.5 billion cubic feet of proven and probable natural-gas reserves and production facilities and some minor oil properties in Saskatchewan.    The transaction is subject to certain conditions and regulatory approvals, it said. </TEXT></DOC>